Zm_bunker_f57_v2

This is the V2 of my map zm_bunker_f57

Changed/added:

- Made more details (Debris etc.)
- There is now an enterance to the bunker (Locked) to make it look more realistic.
- Made the spawn area little bigger to add few more spawnpoints. (60 spawns)
- Tried to fix the doors problem but there may still be some troubles with them.
- Tried to add some more optimision, as there are more details now.
- Fixed few minor mistakes.

This is the last beta for now. I will fix the doors if they cause too much trouble.
